  <summary date="2021-11-23T16:00:38Z" status="Introduced in House">Study To Observe and Prevent (STOP) Human Trafficking Act of 2021

This bill directs the Department of Justice, in coordination with the President's Interagency Task Force to Monitor and Combat Trafficking in Persons, to study and report on the prevalence and instances of human trafficking at adult entertainment clubs in the United States.</summary>
